query:
SELECT s.symbol, s.name, COUNT(t.id) as trade_count 
FROM strategies s 
LEFT JOIN trades t ON s.id = t.strategyId 
GROUP BY s.id, s.symbol, s.name 
ORDER BY s.symbol;
